OL,3,CSara Sharif's father told police 'I've
OL,4,Ckilled my daughter,' court hears
OL,6,FJurors were told Sara was burned by an
OL,7,Firon, scalded by hot water and
OL,8,Fprobably suffered bite marks before
OL,9,Fshe died, ITV News Ellie Pitt reports
OL,10,Ffrom the Old Bailey
OL,12,FThe father of 10-year-old Sara Sharif,
OL,13,Fwho fled to Pakistan after his
OL,14,Fdaughter died, told police "I've
OL,15,Fkilled my daughter," a court has heard.
OL,17,FTaxi driver Urfan Sharif, 42, called
OL,18,Fpolice at 2:47 am about an hour after
OL,19,Fhis family's flight landed in
OL,20,FIslamabad, Pakistan, on August 10 last
OL,21,Fyear.
