OL,3,CSara Sharif's father told police 'I've
OL,4,Ckilled my daughter,' court hears
OL,6,FShortly after, Sara's body was found
OL,7,Fin a bed at a home in Woking, Surrey.
OL,9,FDuring the eight-and-a-half-minute
OL,10,Fcall, a crying Urfan told the
OL,11,Foperator: "I've killed my daughter. I
OL,12,Flegally punished her, and she died."
OL,14,FHe added "she was naughty", saying: "I
OL,15,Fbeat her up, it wasn't my intention to
OL,16,Fkill her, but I beat her up too much."
OL,18,FUrfan stands on trial for murder at
OL,19,Fthe Old Bailey alongside Sara's
OL,20,Fstepmother, Beinash Batool, 30, and
OL,21,Funcle, Faisal Malik, 28.
