OL,3,CSara Sharif's father told police 'I've
OL,4,Ckilled my daughter,' court hears
OL,6,FMr Jones described what police saw at
OL,7,Fthe family home, saying: "In an
OL,8,Fupstairs bedroom, on a bottom bunk
OL,9,Fbed, the police found the body of a
OL,10,Flittle girl, lying in bed, under the
OL,11,Fcover, as if asleep. But she was not
OL,12,Fasleep. She was dead.
OL,14,F"Next to her body was a note in Urfan
OL,15,FSharif's handwriting. It echoed what
OL,16,Fhe had said in that 999 call."
