OL,6,FMr Jones added that Urfan's claim to
OL,7,Fhave beaten up his daughter came
OL,8,F"nowhere near to describing the extent
OL,9,Fof the violence and physical abuse
OL,10,FSara had suffered" for weeks.
OL,12,F"Sara had not just been beaten up. It
OL,13,Fhad been brutal. And throughout, these
OL,14,Fthree defendants were the adults
OL,15,Fliving in the house where Sara had
OL,16,Flived, where she had suffered, and
OL,17,Fwhere she had died," he said.
OL,19,FAll defendants have denied murder.
